### PoImageGc API - HTTP Request File
### Use this file for manual API debugging in VS Code / Visual Studio

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Alive Check (liveness probe)
GET {{baseUrl}}/alive
Accept: application/json

###

### Diagnostics (masked config values)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag
Accept: application/json

###

### Image Analysis Feature Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/images/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Analyze Image - Image Regeneration Mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/images/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageData": "<BASE64_IMAGE_DATA>",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileName": "test-image.jpg",
  "descriptionLength": 350,
  "mode": 0
}

###

### Analyze Image - Meme Generation Mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/images/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageData": "<BASE64_IMAGE_DATA>",
  "contentType": "image/png",
  "fileName": "test-meme.png",
  "descriptionLength": 200,
  "mode": 1
}

###

### OpenAPI Spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json
